  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Before the advent of AI, Computer Based Education (CBE) systems were standalone tools that ran on a local computer to address concerns like student modelling, adaption, and personalization.",
    "With the widespread use of the Internet, new web-based educational tools like e-learning platforms have appeared.",
    "Moreover, new types of adaptive and intelligent systems for educational purposes have been driven by the growing usage of AI techniques.",
    "As a result, there are similarities between CBE and AI in education.",
    "For example, learning management systems (Romero, et al., 2008)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "For example, learning management systems (Romero, et al., 2008)."
  ]
}